# ğŸ“° Fake News Detector

A machine learning application that detects whether news headlines are real or fake using TF-IDF vectorization and Logistic Regression.

## Features

âœ… **Single Headline Analysis** - Check individual headlines with confidence scores
âœ… **Batch Processing** - Upload CSV files to analyze multiple headlines at once
âœ… **Confidence Metrics** - View probability breakdown for each prediction
âœ… **Export Results** - Download predictions as CSV for further analysis
âœ… **Interactive UI** - Built with Streamlit for easy use

